sequenceDiagram
    participant GH as GitHub Issue
    participant N8N as n8n Dispatcher
    participant R as Runner LXC 102
    GH->>N8N: agent:ready label
    N8N->>GH: remove agent:ready, add agent:running
    N8N->>R: SSH Write RUN_INPUT.json
    N8N->>R: SSH Start runner script
    R->>R: Generate evidence files
    N8N->>R: SSH Read status.json
    N8N->>GH: Post evidence comment
    N8N->>GH: Set agent:needs-review + evidence:attached
